OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779872691
OL,3,CPost Office scandal criminal probe
OL,4,Cfaces long delay without #16m funding
OL,5,Cboost
OL,7,FThe criminal investigation into the
OL,8,FPost Office Horizon scandal faces a
OL,9,F#16 million shortfall in funding,
OL,10,Fwhich could delay the police inquiry
OL,11,Fby as much as five years.
OL,13,FThe Home Office has provided a special
OL,14,Fgrant of #2.8 million, while the
OL,15,Fprojected budget for the investigation
OL,16,Fis up to #19.3 million "for 2026/27
OL,17,Fand beyond", Commander Stephen
OL,18,FClayman, who is leading the national
OL,19,Fpolice inquiry - known as Operation
OL,20,FOlympos - has warned.
OL,26,@xD@XOUyD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
