OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779872691
OL,3,CPost Office scandal criminal probe
OL,4,Cfaces long delay without #16m funding
OL,5,Cboost
OL,7,FIn order to submit files for charging
OL,8,Fdecisions by late next year or early
OL,9,F2028, the size of the investigation
OL,10,Fteam needs to nearly double from 111
OL,11,Fto 210, Mr Clayman said.
OL,13,FHe said the "hugely complex" inquiry
OL,14,Finto the scandal involved more than
OL,15,Feight million documents that need to
OL,16,Fbe forensically reviewed.
OL,26,@uD@MOUuD@\O]
