OL,3,CPost Office scandal criminal probe
OL,4,Cfaces long delay without #16m funding
OL,5,Cboost
OL,7,FSo far this year, police have
OL,8,Finterviewed seven more suspects under
OL,9,Fcaution, meaning 13 out of 53 people
OL,10,Funder investigation have been
OL,11,Fquestioned.
OL,13,FThe government said it was
OL,14,F"considering requests for further
OL,15,Ffunding".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
