OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779872691
OL,3,CPost Office scandal criminal probe
OL,4,Cfaces long delay without #16m funding
OL,5,Cboost
OL,7,FAround 1,000 people were wrongly
OL,8,Fprosecuted after Fujitsu's defective
OL,9,FHorizon accounting system, used by the
OL,10,FPost Office, made it appear that money
OL,11,Fwas missing at branches run by
OL,12,Fsubpostmasters.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779872691
OL,3,CPost Office scandal criminal probe
OL,4,Cfaces long delay without #16m funding
OL,5,Cboost
OL,7,FBetween 1999 and 2015, more than 900
OL,8,Fsubpostmasters were prosecuted after
OL,9,Ffaulty Horizon accounting software
OL,10,Fmade it look as though money was
OL,11,Fmissing from their accounts, in what
OL,12,Fis thought to be one of the worst
OL,13,Fmiscarriages of justice in British
OL,14,Flegal history.
OL,16,FA total of 236 sub-postmasters were
OL,17,Fsent to prison. Others were
OL,18,Ffinancially ruined, shunned by their
OL,19,Fcommunities and some took their lives.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779872691
OL,3,CPost Office scandal criminal probe
OL,4,Cfaces long delay without #16m funding
OL,5,Cboost
OL,7,FThe long-running battle for justice
OL,8,Faccelerated dramatically after ITV
OL,9,Fbroadcast the drama Mr Bates Vs The
OL,10,FPost Office.
OL,12,FIn a statement issued to the media
OL,13,Fafter investigators had given victims
OL,14,Fan update on Tuesday, Mr Clayman said:
OL,16,F"Put simply, we do not have the luxury
OL,17,Fof time and must provide answers as
OL,18,Fsoon as possible to those who so
OL,19,Fdesperately deserve them."
OL,26,@xD@AOU{D@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779872691
OL,3,CPost Office scandal criminal probe
OL,4,Cfaces long delay without #16m funding
OL,5,Cboost
OL,7,F"Only by doing this can we piece
OL,8,Ftogether exactly what happened,
OL,9,Festablish who knew what and understand
OL,10,Fthe role suspects may have played," he
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,F"As we have always said, the threshold
OL,14,Fto bring criminal charges is high, so
OL,15,Fwe must be confident that the evidence
OL,16,Fwe present to the Crown Prosecution
OL,17,FService (CPS) has the best possible
OL,18,Fchance of meeting this bar."
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@cO]uD@AOUzD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779872691
OL,3,CPost Office scandal criminal probe
OL,4,Cfaces long delay without #16m funding
OL,5,Cboost
OL,7,FHe continued: "We cannot underestimate
OL,8,Fthe task in hand. Through the many
OL,9,Fconversations we've had with
OL,10,Fsubpostmasters over the course of our
OL,11,Finvestigation so far, we have been
OL,12,Fhonest about these challenges and the
OL,13,Fscale of what lies ahead.
OL,26,@oD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779872691
OL,3,CPost Office scandal criminal probe
OL,4,Cfaces long delay without #16m funding
OL,5,Cboost
OL,7,F"This includes overcoming funding
OL,8,Fchallenges at a time when police
OL,9,Fforces are already severely stretched.
OL,10,FTo meet our proposed timeline of
OL,11,Fsubmitting files for charging
OL,12,Fdecisions in late 2027/early 2028, we
OL,13,Fneed to double the size of the
OL,14,Finvestigation team from 111 to 210.
OL,16,F"Without this, we risk our timelines
OL,17,Fbeing pushed back by as much as five
OL,18,Fyears, which we know is unacceptable
OL,19,Ffor those who have already been living
OL,20,Fwith this for decades.
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779872691
OL,3,CPost Office scandal criminal probe
OL,4,Cfaces long delay without #16m funding
OL,5,Cboost
OL,7,F"We recently received a Home Office
OL,8,Fspecial grant of #2.8 million which
OL,9,Fgoes some way to supporting our costs,
OL,10,Fbut the reality is that we urgently
OL,11,Fneed additional and sustained funding
OL,12,Fto meet our projected budget of up to
OL,13,F#19.3 million for 2026/27 and beyond.
OL,15,F"Dedication, meticulous attention to
OL,16,Fdetail and an unwavering focus on the
OL,17,Fgoal of delivering justice remains at
OL,18,Fthe heart of the team, but we must
OL,19,Fhave the appropriate resources in
OL,20,Fplace to support them."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU|D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779872691
OL,3,CPost Office scandal criminal probe
OL,4,Cfaces long delay without #16m funding
OL,5,Cboost
OL,7,FA government spokesperson said: "The
OL,8,FPost Office Horizon IT scandal was an
OL,9,Fappalling injustice. It is important
OL,10,Fthat victims' voices are heard and
OL,11,Fthat the causes identified through the
OL,12,Fpublic inquiry, and full and fair
OL,13,Fredress is paid out quickly to those
OL,14,Fwho suffered.
OL,26,@oD@aOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779872691
OL,3,CPost Office scandal criminal probe
OL,4,Cfaces long delay without #16m funding
OL,5,Cboost
OL,7,F"In addition, the National Police
OL,8,FChiefs' Council and the Metropolitan
OL,9,FPolice Service are carrying out an
OL,10,Finvestigation into potential
OL,11,Fcriminality in the prosecutions of sub-
OL,12,Fpostmasters and the wider presentation
OL,13,Fof the Horizon IT system as robust.
OL,15,F"That investigation is ongoing. The
OL,16,FHome Office has provided #3.2 million
OL,17,Fsince 2023 to the MPS for Op Olympos
OL,18,Fand has allocated a further #2.8
OL,19,Fmillion in 26/27 and is considering
OL,20,Frequests for further funding."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU|D@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
